summary: The video showcases various meals, including eggs, bacon, avocado, fruit, steak, potatoes, cottage cheese, and yogurt with berries and peanut butter. On-screen text states, "pov: your lifestyle is considered a 'diet'." The narrator comments on societal views regarding food and dieting.
transcript: Doesn't it seem so strange that our society eats so much junk food that eating real food is considered dieting?
